                                    },
                                    "PlannedProgram": {
                                        "CurrentYear": {
                                            "Funding": {
                                                "val": "0.580"
                                            },
                                            "Articles": {
                                                "val": "0"
                                            },
                                            "Text": {
                                                "val": "Continue development of Fiber Optic Cable Plant Monitoring System under SBIR Phase II and transition to Phase III.\n\nContinue HES-C A\/C plant development\/procurement for installation in LPDs 26-28.\n\nContinue SSDG Lube Oil & Fuel Oil Filter class design improvement studies.\n\nInitiate shipboard studies for LPD 28 HM&E obsolescence and new commercial systems.  Develop design, qualification, and testing projects to evaluate:  expanded use of commercial systems for cost savings; and machinery\/engineering control system integration with new systems and networks; MPDE Exhaust duct temperature studies and structural analysts for class improvements.\n \nInitiate shipboard tests for Additive Manufacturing (3D Printing) of HM&E parts.\n\nContinue Reliability and Obsolescence studies."
